Package: evalbehtransmission
Title: Evaluation of nowcasting and forecasting using behavioural data including CoMix and Google Mobility
Version: 0.0.0.1000
Authors@R:
  c(person(given = "Luke",
           family = "Burton",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "luke.burton1@student.lshtm.ac.uk",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-3168-0413"))
           )
Description: Code to process and analyse behavioural data, followed by fitting models to COVID-19 incidence in the UK using different individual and combinations of behavioural datasets. 
Models are evaluated using forecast performance to identify the combination of data streams that best explains changes in transmission dynamics. 
